high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the tumbler from the left side of the counter
Move left to take the tumbler to the fridge.
Chill the tumbler in the fridge, then remove it.
Take the tumbler to the tall cupboard directly behind you.
Put the tumbler away in the bottom half of the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tumbler into a kitchen cupboard.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the left of the oven
Grab the cup off of the counter
Turn left and go to the fridge
Cool the cup in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the large cabinets
Put the cup in the bottom cabinet
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold cup in a cabinet

high_descs: Take two steps forward then turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the clear glass that's in front of you to the left of the silver ware..
Take a step to your left to face the fridge.
Chill the glass in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the cabinet in front of you.
Open the cabinet near the floor and put the glass in there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass in the cabinet.
